description: This is Isis's first match. Say hi to the US champion Janay. Isis is strong, quick, and determined. However, Ice is the Champion for a reason. So why pair these two together? If you step into US your going to earn your dues, Isis learns, but what she learns will be evident in her next match. Prepare for the pummeling.
title: Ice (7-0) vs. The Goddess (0-0).
